data.description: Welcome to this charming Federal-style townhome situated in the desirable Boston Courts community of Dundalk. Boasting 3 bedrooms, 2 full baths, and 2 half baths, this meticulously maintained property offers a comfortable and convenient lifestyle. Step inside to discover laminated flooring throughout the main level, where you'll find a spacious living room and a newly remodeled gourmet kitchen. The kitchen features vinyl flooring, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, stylish backsplash, ample cabinet space, and a cozy table area perfect for casual dining. A slider leads from the kitchen to an outdoor deck, offering a serene space for relaxation or entertainment. Completing the main level is a convenient half bath. Upstairs, the upper level hosts a luxurious primary bedroom with a vaulted ceiling, attached bath, and walk-in closet, providing a private retreat. Two additional bedrooms, one with carpet and the other with vinyl flooring, share a full bath. The lower level offers additional living space with a den and family room, both adorned with laminated flooring. Stay cozy in the family room with an electric fireplace, perfect for chilly evenings. A laundry closet and half bath add convenience to this level. Outside, enjoy the privacy of the fenced yard featuring a deck with a retractable awning, ideal for outdoor gatherings. A shed provides extra storage space for your convenience. Conveniently located near grocery stores, shopping centers, restaurants, and more, this home offers the perfect blend of convenience and community living. Don't miss the opportunity to make this beautiful townhome your own!
